  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK703">
<l>kuṟippiṟ kuṟippuṇar vārai yuṟuppiṉuḷ </l>
<l>yātuṅ koṭuttuk koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The king should ever give whatever (is asked) of his belongings and secure him who, by the indications (of his own mind) is able to read those of another.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
